title: Incroyable mais vrai
plot: Incroyable mais vrai: Directed by Quentin Dupieux. With Alain Chabat, Léa Drucker, Benoît Magimel, Anaïs Demoustier. Alain and Marie moved to the suburb house of their dreams. But the real estate agent warned them: what is in the basement may well change their lives forever.
